{
  "id": "63835a10e7dc93001dc48478",
  "title": "輾転反側",
  "created": 1669552658,
  "updated": 1686886815,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "63835a10e7dc93001dc48478",
      "text": "輾転反側",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1669552658,
      "updated": 1669552658
    },
    {
      "id": "63835a11e600350000a9feb4",
      "text": "てんてんはんそく",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1669552658,
      "updated": 1669552659
    },
    {
      "id": "63835a12e600350000a9feb5",
      "text": "> 何度も[寝返り]を打つこと。[心配]ごとや[悩み]ごとを抱えたり[恋]する人を思ったりして、眠れない様子を表す語。▽「輾転」「反側」はともに寝返りを打つこと。「輾」は「展」とも書く。",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1669552659,
      "updated": 1669552659
    },
    {
      "id": "63835a12e600350000a9feb6",
      "text": "> 出典『[詩経]』[周南関雎]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1669552659,
      "updated": 1669552659
    },
    {
      "id": "63835a12e600350000a9feb7",
      "text": "[https://dictionary.goo.ne.jp/word/輾転反側/ 輾転反側(てんてんはんそく)の意味・使い方 - 四字熟語一覧 - goo辞書]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1669552659,
      "updated": 1669552659
    },
    {
      "id": "63835a12e600350000a9feb8",
      "text": "　[関雎]は「かんしょ」と読む",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1669552659,
      "updated": 1686886815
    },
    {
      "id": "638360eb5e90c00000dc7cc0",
      "text": " 　[https://gyazo.com/d33052bc69b706d6978f0fd0b06ed56f]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1669554411,
      "updated": 1669554412
    },
    {
      "id": "638360ec5e90c00000dc7cc1",
      "text": "  [https://dl.ndl.go.jp/info:ndljp/pid/1047054/16 経書大講. 第6巻 詩經上 - 国立国会図書館デジタルコレクション]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1669554412,
      "updated": 1669554427
    },
    {
      "id": "63835a12e600350000a9feb9",
      "text": "　[https://ja.wikisource.org/wiki/詩経/関雎 詩経/関雎 - Wikisource]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1669552659,
      "updated": 1669552659
    },
    {
      "id": "63835a12e600350000a9feba",
      "text": "　　[漢詩]の[書き下し文]あり",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1669552659,
      "updated": 1669552659
    },
    {
      "id": "63835a12e600350000a9febb",
      "text": "　[https://zh.wikisource.org/wiki/詩經/關雎 詩經/關雎 - 维基文库，自由的图书馆]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1669552659,
      "updated": 1669552659
    },
    {
      "id": "63835a12e600350000a9febc",
      "text": "　　日本語版より詳しい情報が載っている(はず)",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1669552659,
      "updated": 1669552659
    },
    {
      "id": "63835a12e600350000a9febd",
      "text": "　　[機械翻訳]では意味がよく分からない...[hatori.icon]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1669552659,
      "updated": 1669552659
    },
    {
      "id": "63835a12e600350000a9febe",
      "text": "　[https://kanbun.info/syubu/shikyo_kansho.html 関雎（『詩経』国風・周南） - Web漢文大系]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1669552659,
      "updated": 1669552659
    },
    {
      "id": "63835a12e600350000a9febf",
      "text": "  詳しい解説あり",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1669552659,
      "updated": 1669552659
    },
    {
      "id": "63835a12e600350000a9fec0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1669552659,
      "updated": 1669552659
    },
    {
      "id": "63835a12e600350000a9fec1",
      "text": "[https://ja.wiktionary.org/wiki/輾転反側 輾転反側 - ウィクショナリー日本語版]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1669552659,
      "updated": 1669552659
    },
    {
      "id": "63835a12e600350000a9fec2",
      "text": "> 1. 何度も寝返りを打つこと。",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1669552659,
      "updated": 1669552659
    },
    {
      "id": "63835a12e600350000a9fec3",
      "text": "> 2. 解決策が見つからず、悩み続けること。",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1669552659,
      "updated": 1669552659
    },
    {
      "id": "63835a12e600350000a9fec4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1669552659,
      "updated": 1669552659
    },
    {
      "id": "63835a12e600350000a9fec5",
      "text": "[長恨歌]にも引かれている有名な語句[cFQ2f7LRuLYP.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1669552659,
      "updated": 1669552996
    },
    {
      "id": "63835b645e90c00000dc7cb0",
      "text": " >臨邛の道士　鴻都の客",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1669552996,
      "updated": 1669553046
    },
    {
      "id": "63835b965e90c00000dc7cb1",
      "text": " >能く精誠を以て魂魄を致す",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1669553046,
      "updated": 1669553067
    },
    {
      "id": "63835bab5e90c00000dc7cb2",
      "text": " >君王の[* 輾転]の思いを感ぜしめんが為に",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1669553067,
      "updated": 1669553088
    },
    {
      "id": "63835bc15e90c00000dc7cb3",
      "text": " >遂に方士をして慇懃に覓めしむ",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1669553088,
      "updated": 1669553131
    },
    {
      "id": "63835b565e90c00000dc7caf",
      "text": "  [http://kininaruart.com/artist/chogonka/cho10.html 長恨歌と絵画：第十段 - 気になるアート.com]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1669552982,
      "updated": 1669553141
    },
    {
      "id": "63835c165e90c00000dc7cb7",
      "text": "  臨邛生まれの、魂魄に自信ありの道士がいた",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1669553173,
      "updated": 1669553203
    },
    {
      "id": "63835bf55e90c00000dc7cb5",
      "text": "  亡くなった[楊貴妃]を求めて輾転反側している君主を気の毒に思った侍臣が、この道士に頼んで楊貴妃の魂を探させたのだった",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1669553141,
      "updated": 1669553256
    },
    {
      "id": "63835cc25e90c00000dc7cb8",
      "text": " 詩経・長恨歌ともにすごく重要な古典で、この「貴人が寝返りを打つ」エッセンス（モチーフ）は日本古典文学の表現の裏に流れている印象",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1669553346,
      "updated": 1669555672
    },
    {
      "id": "63835d0c5e90c00000dc7cb9",
      "text": "  >しきたへの枕動きて夜も寝じ思ふ人には後もあふものぞ（万葉・2515）",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1669553420,
      "updated": 1669553458
    },
    {
      "id": "638361b75e90c00000dc7cc3",
      "text": "  > 山川　険易の路　展転として　閨中を憶ふ（[懐風藻]・[石上乙麻呂]）",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1669554615,
      "updated": 1669554720
    },
    {
      "id": "638362225e90c00000dc7cc4",
      "text": "   「秋日閨情」（秋の夜に恋しい人を思う詩）。山と川に隔たれて愛する人に会えず、寝返りを打って相手のことを思いやる",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1669554722,
      "updated": 1669554808
    },
    {
      "id": "63835d335e90c00000dc7cbb",
      "text": "  >「臣は神仙の道を得たり。遙に君王展転（デンテン）の御思を知れり」(太平記・三七・畠山入道道誓謀叛事)",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1669553459,
      "updated": 1669553565
    },
    {
      "id": "63835bec5e90c00000dc7cb4",
      "text": "   これは長恨歌の影響下かな",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1669553132,
      "updated": 1669554939
    },
    {
      "id": "6383697b5e90c00000acc3a9",
      "text": "    あたりだった。",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1669556603,
      "updated": 1669556608
    },
    {
      "id": "638369145e90c00000acc3a7",
      "text": "     畠山入道の行いが[楊国忠]・[安禄山]のそれと同じだよねー",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1669556499,
      "updated": 1669556612
    },
    {
      "id": "638369845e90c00000acc3aa",
      "text": "     というとこから楊貴妃の話をしてる",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1669556612,
      "updated": 1669556616
    },
    {
      "id": "638369895e90c00000acc3ab",
      "text": "     道士が出てくるくだりにあるのが[\" 臣は神仙の道を得たり～]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1669556616,
      "updated": 1669556647
    },
    {
      "id": "63835d9e5e90c00000dc7cbf",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1669553565,
      "updated": 1669553565
    },
    {
      "id": "638367c85e90c00000acc3a4",
      "text": "  >宵は耿介にして寝ねず。独り華省に展転す（秋興賦・[潘岳]）",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1669556167,
      "updated": 1669556285
    },
    {
      "id": "638368335e90c00000acc3a6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1669556275,
      "updated": 1669556290
    },
    {
      "id": "638367c95e90c00000acc3a5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1669556168,
      "updated": 1669556168
    },
    {
      "id": "63835a12e600350000a9fec6",
      "text": "関連項目",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1669552659,
      "updated": 1669552659
    },
    {
      "id": "63835a12e600350000a9fec7",
      "text": "　[不眠]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1669552659,
      "updated": 1669552659
    },
    {
      "id": "63835a12e600350000a9fec8",
      "text": "　[四字熟語]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1669552659,
      "updated": 1669552659
    }
  ]
}